Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.56,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What a miserable sight you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.65,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Such sloppy work, and letting your blood  be spilled.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.19,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,You are the disgrace of Circus.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.07,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Kiichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.44,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Why is someone from the First Ship here...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.45,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Just because the enemy was an acquaintance of someone you know,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.45,0:03:47.20,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,you hesitated to put him to rest and instead had the tables turned on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.62,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,You're so soft that it makes me sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.38,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.38,0:04:03.01,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Having someone like you share the same rank as an elite like me, Kiichi, is so annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.01,0:04:07.56,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Oh, good job being a decoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.46,0:04:41.92,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Yotaka...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.72,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yogi is hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.69,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubame-chan is crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.90,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun, well…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.95,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You look badly hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.41,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.87,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks for asking.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.67,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gareki isn't hurt badly.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.97,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not crying, but I think he's just holding it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.84,0:05:31.39,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not hurt either, yet I feel a tightness in my chest.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.89,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like feeling sad...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.27,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I feel this way?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.69,0:05:39.19,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when I think of that man, I feel sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.40,0:05:46.57,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get a cold feeling right here and it hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.87,0:06:01.04,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,A coward who never comes out to act in\N person but enjoys tormenting the weak,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.59,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,as noted on the First Ship's wanted list.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.76,0:06:11.05,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,When your pet grew unexpectedly strong and hurt Yogi,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.05,0:06:15.06,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,did you get carried away and miss the chance to escape?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.02,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,It’s fun to torment others, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.98,0:06:22.73,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.65,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Your girls are great.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.53,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,You control them well.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.24,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Capture completed, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.24,0:07:19.29,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I deeply appreciate your cooperation, Second Ship Captain, Hirato-dono.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.08,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,You're so full of nonsense.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.63,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Return.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.47,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,That's so unkind,{\alpha&HFF&} I was just thanking you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.10,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,That's so unkind, I was just thanking you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.78,0:07:56.24,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Yogi-san, are you with\N that person who killed Yotaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.12,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.12,0:08:04.04,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Wait, Tsubame, they are members of Circus.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.54,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Circus?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.21,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You know about Circus, don’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.80,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,The elite group of people who hunt down criminals.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.18,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I happened to get involved with these people,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.47,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,and learned that there are monsters called Varuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.60,0:08:26.15,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,They killed Tsubaki and turned Yotaka into that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.69,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Gareki-kun, I will tell her the rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.70,0:08:39.33,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,The organization that’s creating Varuga\N is called Kafka by the government.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.20,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,There are two distinct kinds of Varuga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.62,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,One kind is created by Kafka\N itself by repeated cell fusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.04,0:08:52.84,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,And the other kind transforms due to damage to their\N cells caused by Varuga blood or body fluid.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.68,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,They're originally victims, just like Yotaka-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.31,0:09:05.23,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,The drug Yotaka-kun was forced to take was\N probably implanted with Varuga cells.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.86,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,The drug.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.52,0:09:12.40,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Varuga have an extremely fast cell renewal cycle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.44,0:09:16.57,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Even if they get badly hurt, they'll recover in a few days.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.29,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,In order to support that rapid metabolic system,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.29,0:09:24.54,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)}they devour others and integrate the cells of their victims into themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.12,0:09:32.80,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Circus' mission is to eliminate all Varugas,\N put them to rest, and to annihilate Kafka.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.84,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Our role is to end the lives of those...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.18,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,who were made to undergo twisted\N evolution based on the desires of others,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.64,0:09:43.31,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,and set them free from all their chains.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.61,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. "Set them free" is too nice a way to say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.19,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,That's what we were told,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.32,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,but in the end,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.95,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,we're just killing people who turned into Varuga...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.83,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,because we can't return them to how they were before.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.75,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.29,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,kill me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.17,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.63,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Kill me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.80,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.89,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You're not a Varuga!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.35,0:10:31.44,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I was taking that drug for a while too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.57,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I may transform some day.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.57,Default,Na,0,0,0,,Tsubame-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.16,0:10:48.04,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Also, Yotaka isn't here anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.17,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I don’t want to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.38,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I don't like that.{\alpha&HFF&} I'm scared of being alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.80,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I don't like that. I'm scared of being alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.80,0:11:01.05,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Tsubaki-oneechan died, and Grandpa who\N was in the hospital forgot all about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.68,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,And now, Yotaka has died too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.81,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Even so, your grandfather is still alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.81,0:11:12.19,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Didn't the two of you work really hard in order to pay the hospital fees?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.02,0:11:16.69,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,The money we earned wasn't nearly enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.19,0:11:23.28,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,But apparently, Grandpa's old friend had been paying part of the fees.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.70,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,That's what the nurse secretly told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.16,0:11:30.00,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,So he'll be fine even if I'm gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.21,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I just want to disappear...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.13,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Tsubame...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.72,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsubame-chan is crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.72,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drip, drop.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.77,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost as if she's sinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.86,0:12:02.11,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Kii-chan, did you find anything over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.91,0:12:07.28,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,There are lots of research materials,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.28,0:12:11.83,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,but nothing indicates his connection with Kafka.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.42,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Sheesh, they really have their bases covered.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.96,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,I didn't think they would leave any evidence from the beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.96,0:12:23.22,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,But I can't help but admire them for the extreme care they take.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.64,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Even if they're the enemy,\N I cannot help but praise them.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.97,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Jiki-kun, what are you thinking, admiring the enemy?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.35,0:12:36.11,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Well, the only thing left to do\N is to ask him directly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.74,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What a sorry sight you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.82,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,You sound just like Akari-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.45,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,That's not the way you should address\N someone who's 6 years older than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.70,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Show him respect and call him "sensei."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.58,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.58,0:12:58.79,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Oh right, speaking of Akari-sensei, he found\N an interesting notebook in the Niji Forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.38,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Let’s have a tea party with the three of us to discuss that notebook.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.34,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Your "tea" means alcohol, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.14,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.89,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Akari-san won’t come if I'm around.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.85,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Hey, you didn't address him as "sensei" either!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.56,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I'm an exception, because he doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.19,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.86,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,Please finish the job in front of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.61,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Have you been fooling around all this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.03,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.62,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,So did you find anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.74,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.74,0:13:35.12,Default,Ji,0,0,0,,That's why we thought that there's no other way\N except to ask this creature here directly.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.12,0:13:38.79,Default,Ki,0,0,0,,Although, I don't think he'll answer our questions willingly.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.88,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Let's try asking anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.38,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I'll give you a chance to atone for your sins.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.93,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Tell me everything about what you aimed to achieve with your actions,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.64,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,and how you're related to Kafka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.89,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Were you the one who distributed the drug?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.64,Default,Me,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.11,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.44,Default,Me,0,0,0,,Foolish humans like you...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.44,0:14:05.99,Default,Me,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.20,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Tell me about your relationship with Palnedo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.26,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Hirato and the others are putting him to rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.34,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,They've defeated that man.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.01,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's dead...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.14,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man who caused the deaths of Tsubaki and Yotaka is dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.86,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}This should've been what I had strongly wished for.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.40,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.70,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gareki's heart is feeling the same as me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.54,Default,Na,0,0,0,,{\i1}A feeling of tightness...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.12,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if the reason I can't put my feelings to rest is because...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.41,0:15:02.67,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't get to kill him with my own hands...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.76,Default,Uro,0,0,0,,Meiga has been wiped out by them.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.97,Default,Pa,0,0,0,,Meiga?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.94,Default,Pa,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.20,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.57,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Nai?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.91,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about Gareki.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.45,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,He was on that ship, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.75,0:15:41.87,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,The ship that we sank back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.63,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,I guess everything is predestined by fate, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.81,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.52,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,Hirato-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.57,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,You look like there's something you want to say,{\alpha&HFF&} Yogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.69,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,You look like there's something you want to say, Yogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.32,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Back in the Niji Forest, Gareki was attacked by the bestial Varuga,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.99,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,and yet he was unhurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.83,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,From this, we deduced that they wanted to abduct him,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.58,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,so we used him as bait.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.55,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,The members from the First Ship were originally\N in charge of the events that occurred here,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.55,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,but you said you were coming here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.84,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,So you were partly here as a loan to the First Ship\N members in order to attract the attention of that coward.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.84,0:16:39.01,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Also, if the ones who attacked Gareki appeared as well,\N we would be killing two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.31,Default,Yo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Gareki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.61,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,About what? That's part of your job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.24,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.45,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Well now,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.37,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,may I ask you to come along with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.12,0:17:02.87,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.50,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,What are you–
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.05,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Tsubame...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.38,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Why are you going with them?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.85,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You're not alone, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.89,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Grandpa's still...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.77,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,You'll still have people around–
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.77,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Even you, Gareki...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.32,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Even you left me and went somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.11,0:17:37.53,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,There's no one who remains by my side any more.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.21,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Why did you leave us?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.83,0:17:54.30,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,We felt so lonely at home after you disappeared...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.32,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be waiting here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.74,Default,Ts,0,0,0,,Just take your time to talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.99,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Thank you for being so considerate.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.33,Default,Nur,0,0,0,,I don't believe it! Someone from Circus?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.33,Alt,Nur2,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.33,Default,Nur3,0,0,0,,He's so cool, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.59,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.59,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,It's Tsubame.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.18,0:18:44.68,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Grandpa, I've decided to leave the village.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.68,0:18:48.39,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,I think it's possible I won't be able to come here again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.60,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,But, don't worry,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.36,0:18:56.53,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,because the people of Circus will be taking good care of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.66,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Grandpa, please live to a ripe old age, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.70,Default,Nur,0,0,0,,I wonder who the old man in this ward is,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.50,Default,Nur,0,0,0,,to have Circus come here for his sake?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.62,Default,Nur2,0,0,0,,Even the young man who paid his\N hospital fees is such a mystery.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.92,Default,Nur,0,0,0,,Which young man?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.38,Default,Nur2,0,0,0,,He also came by here yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.09,Default,Nur2,0,0,0,,I think he's still in his teens.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.13,Default,Nur2,0,0,0,,He has black hair, and looks really dashing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.97,Default,Nur,0,0,0,,Oh, that young man–
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.14,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.39,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,What's his name?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.39,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.35,0:19:35.32,Default,Nur2,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, when your grandfather was still conscious,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.90,Default,Nur2,0,0,0,,I heard him calling the man "Gareki"...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.32,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.74,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Where's Gareki?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.08,0:19:53.46,Default,Yot,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think Gareki is hanging out with bad\N company and doing dangerous stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.71,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.75,Default,Yot,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget about him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.67,Default,Yot,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a complete stranger to us now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.02,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,Gareki!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.19,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Are you finished with your business in Karasuna?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.69,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,I could've settled everything for you if you had just told me...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.57,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,that you were going to renew the lease for this land.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.70,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,Are you trying to safeguard the grave of your family?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.37,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,I have no family.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.84,0:20:41.01,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,The reason why you left them was because\N you didn't want to implicate them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.34,Default,Hi,0,0,0,,What an adorable thing to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.55,Default,Ga,0,0,0,,Shut up.
