Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.74,0:21:14.08,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,I don't mind even if you have\N to hurt me or cut me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.88,Default,Tsb,0,0,0,,I'm willing to offer my body as\N a specimen in order to defeat Kafka!
